{"tid":475122,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"怎樣說仍是國泰  空姐係外地已唔再講廣東話","createTime":"2017-11-21T00:11:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-21T15:17:21.000Z","uid":79563,"like":74,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"5cb0f1cf71b150ec330260fd3a29bc32d8214cac","tid":475122,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T00:11:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171120/large/1511169849_db14.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171120%2Flarge%2F1511169849_db14.jpg&h=2ea6a61a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上周到歐洲出差，由於飛長途機，到埗後各地行家互相問候時都會問到How was your flight?然後就自自然然地再進入一系列空中體驗嘅討論，作為香港人，一定就會被問到近日被恒指公司宣布踢出恒指成份股的國泰（293）。<br />\n<br />\n身邊同樣來自香港的行家們，使是乘商務客艙，最期待乘坐的已不是國泰，而是星航、卡航以及阿聯猶航空，國泰似乎已經沒有了過往的那種光環。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n散子多次到倫敦均是以國泰機來回，十多個小時機程，同樣是商務客位的服務水平只是「標準」。一到「它」認為是用餐時間，管他是凌晨三點定晚上八點，全機開燈查牌，餐車打扙式出動，強光對閣下失效，都好難避過打扙式送餐聲浪，乘客想唔醒都難。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 相反人哋卡塔爾航空，已經做到按乘客需要，提供喚醒及送餐服務。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但最令散子失望嘅係，以前國泰嘅空姐或地勤，對於身在英國嘅香港人，係會講廣東話，甚至有一次，散子在希斯路機場check-in時，遇到一位外藉地勤人員，都會講廣東話，令人在異地港人有遇上鄉里嘅感覺。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 反而近兩次到倫敦都已經全英文，不論是check-in嘅地勤，抑或是機上服務的空姐。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n雖然服務在競爭激烈的情況下，已變得一般，但在大家在努力地「細數」因航不是之時，有無想過，在香港航空仍未成氣候之下，除了國泰尚有哪有一航空公司可以在國際間與其他國家或地區的航空公司一較高下呢？"},{"pid":"38cb03359412461ff278b6da2884aed9e991886e","tid":475122,"uid":51271,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T00:14:41.000Z","msg":"其實CX都幾多非香港cabin crew，有日韓台泰菲馬印<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3254334989ecade378683f67c6158e225b0528b","tid":475122,"uid":121450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T00:24:03.000Z","msg":"ABC"},{"pid":"6039acc0a94bfee9e62291976724bdd388cfa3a2","tid":475122,"uid":85416,"like":112,"dislike":7,"score":105,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T00:25:50.000Z","msg":"講英文都有得投訴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ec7a15e62f10be5933da4a8ebabcb2736807067","tid":475122,"uid":47674,"like":51,"dislike":0,"score":51,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T00:42:21.000Z","msg":"因航不嬲default講英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c64efa5f55bea773aee0d83076c809377acc0188","tid":475122,"uid":20658,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T00:43:44.000Z","msg":"啲人為屌而屌on99"},{"pid":"efe2bc64a298835b71809c0123afaa663cd5559d","tid":475122,"uid":134834,"like":59,"dislike":0,"score":59,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T00:49:05.000Z","msg":"係飛機有空姐對自己講廣東話的確係有種回家既感覺<br />\n亦係唯一其他公司無得同因航比較既野<br />\n不過佢唔講都唔係一個缺失...只係無左個絕對優勢...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c537f4d72b3d287e8f6f4452db26e8ca348f184","tid":475122,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T00:52:00.000Z","msg":"星航business class嗰款座位 劣評如潮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇落闊落 但瞓落就知硬過監獄張床"},{"pid":"97a60f0ef1a5bba4ceeb5275ce93cf1329428062","tid":475122,"uid":7699,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T00:56:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係飛機有空姐對自己講廣東話的確係有種回家既感覺<br />\n亦係唯一其他公司無得同因航比較既野<br />\n不過佢唔講都唔係一個缺失...只係無左個絕對優勢...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n宜家搭長途機 係你主動同佢講唔該/多謝 佢下次再送餐就會記得你同番你講廣東話"},{"pid":"ad4a715eb97204e84384eee907576c909b294476","tid":475122,"uid":82641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T01:03:06.000Z","msg":"Cx 都就快轉送餐"},{"pid":"0c36b895bcbe4f9771c91004202aa8620873f047","tid":475122,"uid":45760,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T01:05:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>係飛機有空姐對自己講廣東話的確係有種回家既感覺<br />\n亦係唯一其他公司無得同因航比較既野<br />\n不過佢唔講都唔係一個缺失...只係無左個絕對優勢...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n宜家搭長途機 係你主動同佢講唔該/多謝 佢下次再送餐就會記得你同番你講廣東話</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可能我個樣似香港人，一係聽到我同老婆講野， 多數用廣東話問我食乜"},{"pid":"08fe9976c469bf83fb51d56bdcd6e2630defaa19","tid":475122,"uid":134834,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T01:06:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>係飛機有空姐對自己講廣東話的確係有種回家既感覺<br />\n亦係唯一其他公司無得同因航比較既野<br />\n不過佢唔講都唔係一個缺失...只係無左個絕對優勢...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n宜家搭長途機 係你主動同佢講唔該/多謝 佢下次再送餐就會記得你同番你講廣東話</blockquote><br />\n因航就算唔係香港空姐係咪都識廣東話???"},{"pid":"d932a98f636dba303814c7d63a6e3177705d7fae","tid":475122,"uid":85416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T01:09:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>係飛機有空姐對自己講廣東話的確係有種回家既感覺<br />\n亦係唯一其他公司無得同因航比較既野<br />\n不過佢唔講都唔係一個缺失...只係無左個絕對優勢...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n宜家搭長途機 係你主動同佢講唔該/多謝 佢下次再送餐就會記得你同番你講廣東話</blockquote><br />\n因航就算唔係香港空姐係咪都識廣東話???</blockquote><br />\n緊係唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05b8cada3b4a75fa073fe6087bb020dad2dcbfbd","tid":475122,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":17,"score":-17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T01:13:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n推普廢粵<br />\n消滅閩粵文化"},{"pid":"c6d759cd3d2f452ffb8688ce6cc45e733575b546","tid":475122,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T01:18:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>係飛機有空姐對自己講廣東話的確係有種回家既感覺<br />\n亦係唯一其他公司無得同因航比較既野<br />\n不過佢唔講都唔係一個缺失...只係無左個絕對優勢...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n宜家搭長途機 係你主動同佢講唔該/多謝 佢下次再送餐就會記得你同番你講廣東話</blockquote><br />\n因航就算唔係香港空姐係咪都識廣東話???</blockquote><br />\n緊係唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有d馬來西亞同台灣crew都識少少廣東話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7e6e5b9c1a6c0a28d09c74c322dcf49de766344","tid":475122,"uid":7699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T01:30:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>係飛機有空姐對自己講廣東話的確係有種回家既感覺<br />\n亦係唯一其他公司無得同因航比較既野<br />\n不過佢唔講都唔係一個缺失...只係無左個絕對優勢...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n宜家搭長途機 係你主動同佢講唔該/多謝 佢下次再送餐就會記得你同番你講廣東話</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可能我個樣似香港人，一係聽到我同老婆講野， 多數用廣東話問我食乜</blockquote><br />\n通常會同我講英文先 如果佢派緊俾其他人嗰陣聽到佢講廣東話我會講番廣東話 如果唔係都係英文算"},{"pid":"bf4cef1c855da16b791c6c4ecfca9f98c85177ee","tid":475122,"uid":86938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T01:35:48.000Z","msg":"坐咁多次佢地通常都係用英文同你講野嫁喔。。"},{"pid":"957cdd68028b4584747c12d4f004de8c2fef52dd","tid":475122,"uid":8478,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T01:40:52.000Z","msg":"講蝗語就話啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講英文有咩所謂"},{"pid":"a0b0a56ff2581c88bba5bf61eba329f73ecc1e38","tid":475122,"uid":22554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T01:51:25.000Z","msg":"好奇日籍CX 空姐同LOCAL 空組人工差幾多, 有D 日籍空組好似係長時間STAY 係香港咁"},{"pid":"95f55fd5d3f34b2f50d5506b19b3db292614b6fd","tid":475122,"uid":67771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T01:52:57.000Z","msg":"而家少左好多港女做"},{"pid":"3cb030e80f8a784bfff9a46f1dcc19ebbaec515f","tid":475122,"uid":8040,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T01:54:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係飛機有空姐對自己講廣東話的確係有種回家既感覺<br />\n亦係唯一其他公司無得同因航比較既野<br />\n不過佢唔講都唔係一個缺失...只係無左個絕對優勢...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nMK Airline 呢方面就好過因航 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為班空姐 d 英文都係MK Level <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但衰就衰在佢係中資企業 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a536f5f21b9d43992d1df3a6bcd07be2c4215ba","tid":475122,"uid":51391,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T02:10:56.000Z","msg":"散子在希斯路機場check-in時，遇到一位外藉地勤人員，都會講廣東話，令人在異地港人有遇上鄉里嘅感覺。<br />\n<br />\n呢個真<br />\n我試過去希斯路同個鬼佬講英文<br />\n佢話:you can speak chinese<br />\n我以為佢吹水繼續用英文<br />\n佢再話:你可以同我講廣東話<br />\n我勁瘀"},{"pid":"21de0c94c0885e7e966ceb215c29a76dab9861ba","tid":475122,"uid":15497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T02:15:53.000Z","msg":"而家因航都冇香港電影睇喇，變撚哂蝗戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3811e5d5152be16fcd0aa753e23ae72b3afc0b02","tid":475122,"uid":144769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T02:24:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"21ecf2f40c67dd7f9c350af3ed0e72310f5aae25","tid":475122,"uid":137717,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T02:25:09.000Z","msg":"係外地都要聽廣東話 唔識聽英文咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9863882f456423da79a089b158f6a192e3e43a12","tid":475122,"uid":4783,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T02:26:15.000Z","msg":"邊個知你識廣東話<img src=\"/assets/faces/no